title: Crystal seed (disambiguation)

properties.name: description
properties.value: Crystal seed may refer to one of the following:

content:
Crystal seed may refer to one of the following:

  • Crystal acorn, a seed which is used to grow crystal trees
  • Crystal armour seed, a seed which is used to create crystal armour
  • Crystal saw seed, a seed which is used to create the crystal saw
  • Crystal seed, the seed which teleports players to Lord Ieuan Amlodd during Song of the Elves
  • Crystal teleport seed, a seed which is used to create teleport crystals
    • Enhanced crystal teleport seed, a seed which is used to create eternal teleport crystals
  • Crystal tool seed, a seed which is used to create crystal tools
  • Crystal weapon seed, a seed which is used to create crystal weapons
    • Enhanced crystal weapon seed, a seed which is used to create the Blade of Saeldor or the Bow of Faerdhinen
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
If an internal link led you to this disambiguation page, you may wish to change the link to point directly to the intended article.
rawContent:
'''Crystal seed''' may refer to one of the following:

*[[Crystal acorn]], a seed which is used to grow [[crystal trees]]
*[[Crystal armour seed]], a seed which is used to create crystal armour
*[[Crystal saw seed]], a seed which is used to create the [[crystal saw]]
*[[Crystal seed]], the seed which teleports players to [[Lord Ieuan Amlodd]] during [[Song of the Elves]]
*[[Crystal teleport seed]], a seed which is used to create [[teleport crystal]]s
**[[Enhanced crystal teleport seed]], a seed which is used to create [[eternal teleport crystal]]s
*[[Crystal tool seed]], a seed which is used to create crystal tools
*[[Crystal weapon seed]], a seed which is used to create crystal weapons
**[[Enhanced crystal weapon seed]], a seed which is used to create the [[Blade of saeldor|Blade of Saeldor]] or the [[Bow of faerdhinen#Charged|Bow of Faerdhinen]]

{{Disambig}}
